Family means everything to me.

237
00:17:20,983 --> 00:17:23,419
我绝不会拿罗宾的性命来冒险
And I will not risk Robin's life

238
00:17:23,452 --> 00:17:25,922
卷入另一场跟你丈夫有关的战争.
to get caught up in another of your husband's wars.

239
00:17:25,955 --> 00:17:28,857
- 我饿了. - 安静, 亲爱的.
- I'm hungry. - Hush now, darling.

240
00:17:28,892 --> 00:17:31,093
你刚刚吃过呀.
You just ate.

241
00:17:31,127 --> 00:17:33,962
