Will you shut up?

259
00:18:46,671 --> 00:18:48,704
这一带到处是山地部落.
There's hill tribes all around here.

260
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:51,208
如果我真的要死了,
If I'm going to die,

261
00:18:51,241 --> 00:18:53,576
我宁愿哼着歌去死.
it may as well be with a song in my heart.

262
00:18:53,612 --> 00:18:56,847
我可以抢走你的食物并把你丢在这里.
I should just take your food and leave you here.

263
00:18:56,882 --> 00:19:00,151
嗯? 那时候你会怎样?
Eh? What would you do then?

264
00:19:00,184 --> 00:19:03,020
