What do you want, Bronn? Gold? Women?

267
00:19:09,461 --> 00:19:12,364
多金的女人?
Golden women?

268
00:19:12,397 --> 00:19:14,599
跟着我, 你要什么有什么,
Stick with me and you'll have them all,

269
00:19:14,634 --> 00:19:17,468
只要有我在, 你很快就能得到你想要的.
for as long as I'm around and not for a moment longer.

270
00:19:17,502 --> 00:19:20,770
你知道这一点.
But you knew that.

271
00:19:20,806 --> 00:19:24,374
所以你才会如此勇敢地为维护我的荣誉而出战.
That is why you so valiantly took up arms to defend my honor.

272
00:19:26,243 --> 00:19:28,578
很公平.
Fair enough.

273
00:19:28,614 --> 00:19:31,148
但别指望我会对你卑躬屈膝...
But don't go looking for me to bend the knee

274
00:19:31,182 --> 00:19:33,751
对你说话时满口老爷大人.
and "My Lord" you every time you take a shit.

275
00:19:33,786 --> 00:19:37,055
我不当你的仆人, 也不当你的朋友.
I'm not your toady and I'm not your friend.

276
00:19:38,191 --> 00:19:40,292
但我珍视你的友谊,
Though I would treasure your friendship,

277
00:19:40,326 --> 00:19:42,929
我主要看重你杀人的身手.
I'm mainly interested in your facility with murder.

278
00:19:42,963 --> 00:19:46,366
