That trinket is worth more than everything your tribe owns.

315
00:22:15,818 --> 00:22:19,189
如果你肯帮我们, 多夫之子夏嘎,
But if you help us, Shagga Son of Dolf,

316
00:22:19,222 --> 00:22:21,892
