Blood will always tell.

327
00:23:15,377 --> 00:23:18,515
你会被吊死的, 野种.
You'll hang for this, bastard.

328
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:41,035
我告诉过你别做傻事.
I told you not to do anything stupid.

329
00:23:41,069 --> 00:23:44,704
