Commander?

337
00:24:48,806 --> 00:24:51,974
( Barks, whines )

338
00:24:52,009 --> 00:24:54,810
待在这里.
Stay.

339
00:25:06,124 --> 00:25:08,358
喂?
Hello?

340
00:25:17,269 --> 00:25:18,303
是谁?
Who's there?

341
00:25:18,336 --> 00:25:19,503
( Whines )

342
00:25:25,111 --> 00:25:28,046
