350
00:26:22,869 --> 00:26:25,538
( Grunts )

351
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:28,708
<i>( Screaming, snarling continue )</i>

352
00:26:32,546 --> 00:26:35,013
他们在干什么?
What did they do?

353
00:26:36,048 --> 00:26:37,311
<i>(羊人最适合当奴隶.)
( Rakharo speaking Dothraki )</i>

354
00:26:37,348 --> 00:26:40,852
(卓戈卡奥会把他们送给奴隶贩子.)

355
00:26:41,348 --> 00:26:43,852
(奴隶贩子会送给我们金钱.)

356
00:26:46,348 --> 00:26:49,852
(还有丝绸和钢铁.)

357
00:26:51,099 --> 00:26:54,469
我以为多斯拉克人不信赖金钱.
Daenerys: I thought the Dothraki didn't believe in money.

358
00:26:54,502 --> 00:26:58,405
金钱可以雇船, 公主,
Gold to hire ships, Princess,

359
00:26:58,440 --> 00:27:01,276
乘船才能去维斯特洛.
ships to sail to Westeros.

360
00:27:04,247 --> 00:27:07,281
<i>( Louder screaming )</i>

361
00:27:17,058 --> 00:27:19,527
乔拉, 叫他们住手.
Jorah, make them stop.

362
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:21,795
- 卡丽熙? - 你听到我的命令了.
- Khaleesi? - You heard me.

363
00:27:21,829 --> 00:27:25,332
这些人为卡奥流血卖命, 如今该他们取得奖赏了.
These men have shed blood for their Khal. Now they claim their rewards.

364
00:27:25,365 --> 00:27:27,468
(她是个羊女, 卡丽煕.)
( Rakharo speaking )

365
00:27:27,566 --> 00:27:29,468
(我们的战士上她是看得起她.)

366
00:27:29,566 --> 00:27:31,468
(要是她的哭嚎冒犯了卡丽煕.)

367
00:27:31,566 --> 00:27:34,468
(我去把她的舌头割了.)

368
00:27:36,179 --> 00:27:38,547
公主, 你的心肠很软,
Princess, you have a gentle heart,

369
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:40,583
<i>但战争就是这个样子.
but this is how it's always been.</i>

370
00:27:40,616 --> 00:27:43,586
我的心肠并不软, 爵士.
I do not have a gentle heart, Ser.

371
00:27:43,616 --> 00:27:46,586
(照我的命令办, 否则卡奥惟你是问)

372
00:27:52,128 --> 00:27:54,395
<i>(住手!)
( Rakharo speaks )</i>

373
00:27:55,999 --> 00:27:58,500
<i>(吾血之血. 她是我的!)
Kash qoy qoyi thira disse. Me qorasokh anni!</i>

374
00:27:58,534 --> 00:28:02,670
<i>- 来吧. - (她是我抓到的!)
- Come. - Man: Anha afichak mae m'arakhoon!</i>

375
00:28:02,703 --> 00:28:06,373
(你小心一点.)
( Speaks Dothraki )

376
00:28:07,909 --> 00:28:09,777
你要怎么处置她?
What do you want done with them?

377
00:28:09,811 --> 00:28:12,378
把她带到我这儿来. 还有那些女人.
Bring her to me. And those women there.

378
00:28:14,249 --> 00:28:16,682
您没法把她们全都收为己有, 公主.
You cannot claim them all, Princess.

379
00:28:16,717 --> 00:28:18,751
我能,
I can,

380
00:28:18,786 --> 00:28:21,488
我就要这样做.
and I will.

381
00:28:21,522 --> 00:28:23,490
(操!)
Man: Me Fati!

382
00:28:23,523 --> 00:28:26,993
(卡丽熙抢了我的战利品,)
Khaleesi vazha anhaan qorasokh anni,

383
00:28:27,028 --> 00:28:29,363
(本该是让我骑的羊女!)
ch'anha afichak mae m'arakhoon anni!

384
00:28:29,396 --> 00:28:32,232
(等我见到她,)
Drogo: Me vastoe hatif anni;

385
00:28:32,267 --> 00:28:34,969
<i>(我会问一下这件事.)
ahhazaan yer Nemo vacchaki.</i>

386
00:28:35,896 --> 00:28:38,632
(我生命中的月亮,)

387
00:28:38,896 --> 00:28:42,632
(马戈说你抢了他的战利品.)

388
00:28:42,896 --> 00:28:46,632
(一个本该让他骑的羊人之女.)

389
00:28:46,896 --> 00:28:49,632
(告诉我是怎么回事.)

390
00:28:50,896 --> 00:28:55,632
(马戈说的是实话, 我的日和星.)

391
00:28:56,396 --> 00:28:58,632
(今天我是收了许多羊女...)

392
00:28:58,797 --> 00:29:00,632
(不让她们被人骑...)

393
00:29:04,297 --> 00:29:05,632
(战争就是这样.)

394
00:29:06,297 --> 00:29:08,632
(现在这些女人是奴隶...)

395
00:29:08,797 --> 00:29:11,632
(...随我们高兴摆布.)

396
00:29:12,797 --> 00:29:14,632
(那我高兴让她们平安.)

397
00:29:15,797 --> 00:29:18,632
(若你的战士要骑她们, 就要将她们收作妻子.)

398
00:29:20,797 --> 00:29:23,231
(马会和羊交配吗?)

399
00:29:24,297 --> 00:29:26,632
(马和羊都是龙的食物!)

400
00:29:28,297 --> 00:29:30,332
(你是个外族人.)

401
00:29:30,797 --> 00:29:32,632
(你无权命令我.)

402
00:29:32,797 --> 00:29:35,632
(我是卡丽熙, 我有权命令你.)

403
00:29:35,896 --> 00:29:38,632
( Drogo snickers )

404
00:29:38,297 --> 00:29:40,632
(看她变得多凶猛?)

405
00:29:41,297 --> 00:29:44,632
(这是因为她怀着我的儿子, 骑着世界的骏马,)

406
00:29:45,896 --> 00:29:47,632
(让她充满火焰.)

407
00:29:48,896 --> 00:29:50,632
(我听明白了.)

408
00:29:51,896 --> 00:29:53,632
(马戈, 找别地方去发泄吧.)

409
00:29:54,348 --> 00:29:55,749
( Spits )

410
00:29:56,297 --> 00:29:59,632
(听从外族女人的卡奥还算是什么卡奥.)

411
00:30:01,021 --> 00:30:03,923
<i>(奥霍斯.)
( Drogo grunts ) Ohos.</i>

412
00:30:05,226 --> 00:30:07,093
<i>(让开.)
Os.</i>

413
00:30:12,326 --> 00:30:16,093
(我不会用火烧掉你的尸体.)

414
00:30:17,326 --> 00:30:20,093
(我不会给你那样的荣耀.)

415
00:30:25,326 --> 00:30:27,792
(我会让甲虫吃你的眼珠.)

416
00:30:27,826 --> 00:30:30,192
(我会让蛆虫爬满你的肺.)

417
00:30:35,826 --> 00:30:39,593
(我会让雨水落在你腐烂的皮肤上...)

418
00:30:40,826 --> 00:30:44,593
(...直到你只剩下一把骨头.)

419
00:30:48,826 --> 00:30:50,593
(你要先杀得死我才行.)

420
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:52,300
(你就要死了.)
( Gasps )

421
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,300
(我的日和星受伤了.)

422
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:16,201
(只是破了点皮...)

423
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:17,201
(...我生命中的月亮.)

424
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,201
(医者在哪儿?)

425
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,201
(让飞虫咬了一口而已.)

426
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:26,433
<i>(我可以帮伟大的骑马战士疗伤.)
( Woman speaking Dothraki )</i>

427
00:31:25,067 --> 00:31:27,134
( Gasps )

428
00:31:27,268 --> 00:31:30,134
(卡奥不需要跟羊交配的女人帮忙.)

429
00:31:32,268 --> 00:31:33,535
(她是我的人, 让她说.)

430
00:31:34,710 --> 00:31:36,845
谢谢您, 银发夫人.
Thank you, silver lady.

431
00:31:39,082 --> 00:31:41,548
你是谁?
Who are you?

432
00:31:41,584 --> 00:31:44,519
我叫弥丽马兹笃尔. 是这座神庙的女祭司.
I am named Mirri Maz Duur. I was the Godswife of this Temple.

433
00:31:44,552 --> 00:31:46,153
(巫魔女.)
( Spits )

434
00:31:46,188 --> 00:31:48,923
我母亲是从前的女祭司.
My mother was Godswife here before me.

435
00:31:48,958 --> 00:31:51,393
她教会我如何调制圣烟和圣膏.
She taught me how to make healing smokes and ointments.

436
00:31:51,426 --> 00:31:54,430
<i>所有人类都是同一群羔羊, 这是我们的信仰.
All men are of one flock, so my people believe.</i>

437
00:31:54,464 --> 00:31:56,566
至高牧神派我到世上医治他的...
The Great Shepherd sent me to Earth to heal his--

438
00:31:56,865 --> 00:32:00,566
(巫魔女太多话了. 会毒害耳朵.)

439
00:32:02,207 --> 00:32:04,208
不论是羔羊或是狮子,
lamb or lion,

440
00:32:04,241 --> 00:32:06,911
他的伤口必须立刻清洗缝针
his wound must be washed and sewn

441
00:32:06,944 --> 00:32:09,211
<i>不然会化脓的.
or it will fester.</i>

442
00:32:10,345 --> 00:32:12,211
(让她给你清洗伤口吧, 我的日和星...)

443
00:32:12,545 --> 00:32:14,612
(看见你流血让我心痛.)

444
00:32:34,002 --> 00:32:36,203
<i>( Men chatting, eating )</i>

445
00:32:37,807 --> 00:32:41,109
三十年来我杀死过...
For 30 years I've been making corpses

446
00:32:41,144 --> 00:32:42,978
无数敌人, 小子.
out of men, boy.

447
00:32:43,012 --> 00:32:45,747
我最适合率领前锋.
I'm the man you want leading the Vanguard.

448
00:32:47,115 --> 00:32:49,282
盖伯特葛洛佛才该率领前锋.
Galbart Glover will lead the Van.

449
00:32:49,317 --> 00:32:51,984
除非他妈的长城整个融化
The bloody Wall will melt

450
00:32:52,019 --> 00:32:55,087
否则安伯家别想走在葛洛佛家前头.
before an Umber marches behind a Glover.

451
00:32:55,923 --> 00:32:58,157
<i>我要率领前锋
I will lead the Van</i>

452
00:32:58,192 --> 00:33:00,492
否则我就带着我的人马
or I will take my men

453
00:33:00,527 --> 00:33:02,627
班师回家.
and march them home.

454
00:33:07,567 --> 00:33:10,236
欢迎你这么做, 安伯大人.
You are welcome to do so, Lord Umber.

455
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:13,339
等我收拾完兰尼斯特家
And when I am done with the Lannisters

456
00:33:13,374 --> 00:33:15,674
我会立刻回师北上,
I will march back North,

457
00:33:15,710 --> 00:33:17,176
把你从你的城堡里抓出来
root you out of your Keep

458
00:33:17,211 --> 00:33:19,881
并当成背誓者吊死.
and hang you for an oathbreaker.

459
00:33:19,914 --> 00:33:21,915
背誓者, 是吗?!
Oathbreaker, is it?!

460
00:33:23,484 --> 00:33:26,054
我可不会干坐着任人侮辱
I'll not sit here and swallow insults

461
00:33:26,087 --> 00:33:28,623
特别是象你这种刚从泥里钻出来的小鬼, 八成连尿都还有青草气.
from a boy so green he pisses grass.

462
00:33:29,657 --> 00:33:31,459
( Snarls )

463
00:33:31,492 --> 00:33:34,194
<i>( Screaming )</i>

464
00:33:42,804 --> 00:33:45,105
我父亲曾教导我必须以死刑惩戒...
My Lord father taught me it was death to bare steel

465
00:33:45,138 --> 00:33:47,207
<i>敢对主君拔剑的封臣.
- against your Liege Lord. - ( Huffs )</i>

466
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:51,545
但我相信大琼恩只是想帮我切肉罢了.
But doubtless the Greatjon only meant to cut my meat for me.

467
00:33:53,582 --> 00:33:56,017
你的肉...
Your meat...

468
00:34:01,156 --> 00:34:03,826
还真他妈的硬.
is bloody tough.

469
00:34:04,728 --> 00:34:06,895
<i>( Chortles )</i>

470
00:34:08,599 --> 00:34:10,967
( All laughing )

471
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:37,429
- 怎么了? 出什么事了? - 嘘, 没什么.
- What is it? What's happened? - Shh, it's all right.

472
00:34:41,902 --> 00:34:45,471
- 你要去哪儿? - 去南方. 去救父亲.
- Where are you going? - South. For father.

473
00:34:45,505 --> 00:34:47,206
可现在是午夜啊.
But it's the middle of the night.

474
00:34:47,240 --> 00:34:49,375
兰尼斯特家的探子无处不在.
The Lannisters have spies everywhere.

475
00:34:49,409 --> 00:34:51,976
我不希望让他们知道我们已经出发.
I don't want them to know we're coming.

476
00:34:52,012 --> 00:34:54,713
他们的人马比我们多.
They have more men than we do.

477
00:34:54,748 --> 00:34:56,949
嗯, 是这样的.
Aye, they do.

478
00:34:56,983 --> 00:34:59,050
我能和你一起去吗?
Can't I come with you?

479
00:34:59,085 --> 00:35:01,586
现在我能骑马了. 你看过我骑马了.
I can ride now. You've seen me riding.

480
00:35:01,621 --> 00:35:03,722
我不会再惹麻烦的, 我...
And I won't get in the way, I--

481
00:35:03,757 --> 00:35:06,291
临冬城必须有史塔克家的人坐镇.
There must always be a Stark at Winterfell.

482
00:35:06,326 --> 00:35:08,460
在我回来之前你就是城主.
Until I return that will be you.

483
00:35:10,931 --> 00:35:14,199
我们走后你绝不能离开城堡. 明白吗?
You are not to leave the castle walls while we are gone. Do you understand?

484
00:35:16,838 --> 00:35:20,206
好好听从鲁温师傅的教导. 好好照顾你的弟弟.
Listen to Maester Luwin. Look after your little brother.

485
00:35:20,242 --> 00:35:22,376
我会的.
I will.

486
00:35:22,411 --> 00:35:24,478
我有时间就会写信回来,
I'll send letters whenever I can,

487
00:35:24,512 --> 00:35:26,748
但如果你很久没收到我的信,
but if you don't hear from me,

488
00:35:26,782 --> 00:35:28,684
也不要担心.
don't be scared.

489
00:35:33,791 --> 00:35:35,992
我会回来的.
Until I return.

490
00:35:56,215 --> 00:35:59,282
你躲在那儿多久了?
How long have you been hiding out there?

491
00:35:59,318 --> 00:36:02,786
罗柏会找你道别.
Robb will be looking for you to say goodbye.

492
00:36:04,123 --> 00:36:06,056
他们全都走了.
They've all gone away.

493
00:36:06,092 --> 00:36:09,027
他们很快就会回来. 罗柏会救出父亲
They'll be back soon. Robb will free father

494
00:36:09,061 --> 00:36:11,262
他们会和母亲一道回来.
and they'll come back with mother.

495
00:36:12,931 --> 00:36:15,434
不, 他们不会.
No, they won't.

496
00:36:20,106 --> 00:36:22,208
<i>请你们务必看顾罗柏.
Bran: Please watch over Robb.</i>

497
00:36:22,242 --> 00:36:24,710
也请你们看顾临冬城所所有人马.
And watch over all the other men from Winterfell.

498
00:36:24,744 --> 00:36:27,913
还有, 还有席恩.
And Theon too, I suppose.

499
00:36:33,619 --> 00:36:36,387
你听见了吗, 孩子?
You hear them, boy?

500
00:36:36,422 --> 00:36:39,023
旧神正在回答你.
The Old Gods are answering you.

501
00:36:39,057 --> 00:36:40,958
你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here?

502
00:36:40,992 --> 00:36:43,862
他们也是我的神.
They're my Gods too.

503
00:36:45,364 --> 00:36:48,967
在长城之外, 他们是惟一的真神.
Beyond the Wall, they're the only Gods.

504
00:36:50,336 --> 00:36:52,639
即便奴隶也可以祈祷.
Even slaves are allowed to pray.

505
00:36:52,672 --> 00:36:55,041
你可不是奴隶.
You're not a slave.

506
00:36:57,110 --> 00:37:00,079
嗯, 你的朋友确实曾经拿刀抵住我的喉咙.
Well, your friend did put a knife to my throat.

507
00:37:01,215 --> 00:37:03,817
我不是在抱怨, 小领主,
I'm not complaining, Little Lord,

508
00:37:03,851 --> 00:37:06,585
只是说出事实.
just telling truths.

509
00:37:07,887 --> 00:37:10,690
你说听见神说话是什么意思?
What did you mean about hearing the Gods?

510
00:37:10,724 --> 00:37:13,059
你向他们祈求,
You asked them,

511
00:37:13,092 --> 00:37:14,726
而他们正在回答.
they're answering you.

512
00:37:14,762 --> 00:37:17,731
嘘.
Shh.

513
00:37:17,764 --> 00:37:19,431
竖起耳朵.
Open your ears.

514
00:37:19,465 --> 00:37:21,867
<i>( Leaves rustling )</i>

515
00:37:24,871 --> 00:37:27,106
不过是风声.
It's only the wind.

516
00:37:27,141 --> 00:37:30,143
你以为这风是谁送来的?
Who do you think sends the wind

517
00:37:30,177 --> 00:37:32,144
如果不是诸神的话?
if not the Gods?

518
00:37:32,179 --> 00:37:33,880
他们能看到你, 孩子.
They see you, boy.

519
00:37:33,914 --> 00:37:36,317
<i>他们也能听到你说话.
They hear you.</i>

520
00:37:36,351 --> 00:37:37,918
<i>( Sighs )</i>

521
00:37:37,952 --> 00:37:40,789
在你哥哥要去的地方, 他们无法帮他.
Your brother will get no help from them where he's going.

522
00:37:40,822 --> 00:37:43,625
旧神在南方没有力量.
The Old Gods have no power in the South.

523
00:37:43,659 --> 00:37:47,329
那儿的鱼梁木早已被砍伐一空.
The Weirwoods there were all cut down a long time ago.

524
00:37:47,364 --> 00:37:50,132
没有眼睛, 他们如何看顾你哥哥呢?
How can they watch when they have no eyes?

525
00:37:50,166 --> 00:37:51,567
<i>( Running footsteps )</i>

526
00:37:53,170 --> 00:37:57,039
嗯, 真是个大块头.
( Osha giggles ) Well, there's a big man.

527
00:37:57,072 --> 00:38:00,242
我敢说他有巨人的血统.
He has giants' blood in him or I'm the Queen.

528
00:38:00,275 --> 00:38:02,643
回去找你的衣服, 阿多.
Go back and find your clothes, Hodor.

529
00:38:02,677 --> 00:38:04,512
<i>去穿衣服吧.
- ( Laughs ) - Go dress.</i>

530
00:38:04,547 --> 00:38:06,079
阿多.
Hodor.

531
00:38:09,217 --> 00:38:11,418
长城之外真的有巨人吗?
Are there really giants beyond the Wall?

532
00:38:12,788 --> 00:38:15,757
有巨人, 还有比巨人更可怕的生物.
Giants and worse than giants.

533
00:38:15,791 --> 00:38:18,760
我跟你哥哥说过,
I tried telling your brother,

534
00:38:18,793 --> 00:38:20,594
他走错方向了.
he's marching the wrong way.

535
00:38:20,628 --> 00:38:24,132
所有的人马, 他们应该去北方, 孩子.
All these swords, they should be going North, boy.

536
00:38:24,166 --> 00:38:26,333
北方, 不是南方!
North, not south!

537
00:38:29,072 --> 00:38:31,472
寒风已然吹起.
The cold winds are rising.

538
00:38:31,507 --> 00:38:33,007
<i>( Leaves rustling )</i>

539
00:38:47,458 --> 00:38:49,793
他们被异鬼做了手脚.
They were touched by White Walkers.

540
00:38:51,329 --> 00:38:53,297
所以他们才会回来.
That's why they came back.

541
00:38:53,331 --> 00:38:56,199
所以他们的眼睛才会变成蓝色.
That's why their eyes turned blue.

542
00:38:56,233 --> 00:38:59,369
只有火能阻止他们.
Only fire will stop them.

543
00:39:01,306 --> 00:39:03,072
你怎么知道的?
How do you know that?

544
00:39:03,108 --> 00:39:04,842
我从书上看到的...
I read about it in a book--

545
00:39:04,876 --> 00:39:07,945
伊蒙师傅的图书馆里的一本非常古老的书.
a very old book in Maester Aemon's library.

546
00:39:10,481 --> 00:39:12,615
那本书还说了些什么?
What else did the book say?

547
00:39:12,650 --> 00:39:14,550
异鬼
The White Walkers

548
00:39:14,585 --> 00:39:17,353
在冰层之下沉睡了数千年.
sleep beneath the ice for thousands of years.

549
00:39:17,387 --> 00:39:19,923
当他们苏醒的时候...
And when they wake up--

550
00:39:20,925 --> 00:39:24,762
当他们苏醒的时候会怎样?
And when they wake up, what?

551
00:39:27,731 --> 00:39:30,233
我希望长城足够高.
I hope The Wall is high enough.

552
00:39:53,157 --> 00:39:55,257
( Men chattering )

553
00:40:02,764 --> 00:40:05,065
是夏雪, 夫人.
Summer snows, My Lady.

554
00:40:05,101 --> 00:40:08,135
罗柏马带来了北境的人马.
Robb's brought the North with him.

555
00:40:14,344 --> 00:40:16,210
河间地的领主们正在败退
The River Lords are falling back

556
00:40:16,246 --> 00:40:18,079
詹姆兰尼斯特在后面穷追不舍.
with Jaime Lannister at their heels.

557
00:40:18,114 --> 00:40:21,516
而泰温大人正带着另一支兰尼斯特军队从南方进逼.
And Lord Tywin is bringing around a second Lannister army from the South.

558
00:40:21,552 --> 00:40:24,320
我们的斥候报告说其规模比弑君者的更庞大.
Our scouts confirm it's even larger than the Kingslayer's.

559
00:40:24,355 --> 00:40:27,625
管他一支还是两支军队, 北境之王...
One army or two, the Kings in the North

560
00:40:27,659 --> 00:40:31,461
能够打垮十倍优势的敌人.
threw back hosts 10 times as large.

561
00:40:34,965 --> 00:40:36,632
母亲!
Mother!

562
00:40:40,038 --> 00:40:42,271
你气色很好.
You look well.

563
00:40:43,773 --> 00:40:47,543
凯特琳夫人, 在此动乱时刻见到您真是高兴.
Lady Catelyn, you're a welcome sight in these troubled times.

564
00:40:47,577 --> 00:40:50,045
我们没想到会在这里见到您, 夫人.
We had not thought to meet you here, My Lady.

565
00:40:51,014 --> 00:40:53,583
我也没想到会来这里.
I had not thought to be here.

566
00:40:53,617 --> 00:40:55,684
我想单独和我儿子讲几句话.
I would speak with my son alone.

567
00:40:55,719 --> 00:40:58,021
相信诸位大人能够理解.
I know you will forgive me, My Lords.

568
00:40:58,056 --> 00:41:00,289
你们听见夫人说的话了! 快动身!
You heard her! Move your asses!

569
00:41:00,324 --> 00:41:02,659
快点, 到外面去.
Come on, out.

570
00:41:02,695 --> 00:41:05,329
你也是, 葛雷乔伊. 你他妈的耳聋了吗?
You too, Greyjoy. Are you bloody deaf?

571
00:41:05,364 --> 00:41:07,266
不要担心, 夫人.
Have no fear, My Lady.

572
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:10,068
<i>我们会拿剑拥穿泰温兰尼斯特的屁眼...
We'll shove our swords up Tywin Lannister's bunghole</i>

573
00:41:10,101 --> 00:41:12,871
然后打下红堡救出奈德.
and then it's on to the Red Keep to free Ned.

574
00:41:12,905 --> 00:41:15,838
- 你这老鬼头, 罗德利克. - 大琼恩.
- You old devil, Rodrik. - Jon.

575
00:41:15,873 --> 00:41:18,208
你的功夫还没荒废, 是吗?
You're not wasting away, are you?

576
00:41:29,452 --> 00:41:32,288
我还清楚地记得你出生那天的样子...
I remember the day you came into this world

577
00:41:32,322 --> 00:41:35,358
脸红红的, 大声哭闹.
red-faced and squalling.

578
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:39,528
现在我却看到你率领着一支大军上战场.
And now I find you leading a host to war.

579
00:41:40,563 --> 00:41:42,965
- 没别人了. - 没别人?
- There was no one else. - No one?

580
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:45,735
我刚才见到的那些人是谁?
Who were those men I saw here?

581
00:41:45,769 --> 00:41:48,838
- 他们都不是史塔克. - 他们都身经百战.
- None of them are Starks. - All of them are seasoned in battle.

582
00:41:48,873 --> 00:41:51,909
如果你想把我送回临冬城...
If you think you can send me back to Winterfell--

583
00:41:51,943 --> 00:41:54,210
哦, 我真希望能这么做.
Oh, would that I could.

584
00:41:57,282 --> 00:41:59,250
我收到了...
There was...

585
00:41:59,284 --> 00:42:01,719
一封信.
a letter.

586
00:42:04,155 --> 00:42:05,590
珊莎写来的.
From Sansa.

587
00:42:06,559 --> 00:42:08,860
你的意思是王后写来的.
From the Queen, you mean.

588
00:42:16,833 --> 00:42:19,936
- 上面没有提到艾莉亚. - 确实没有.
- There's no mention of Arya. - No.

589
00:42:30,547 --> 00:42:32,880
你带来多少人?
How many men do you have?

590
00:42:32,914 --> 00:42:35,317
一万八千.
18,000.

591
00:42:35,351 --> 00:42:37,818
如果我去君临向乔佛里屈膝下跪...
If I go to King's Landing and bend my knee to Joffrey--

592
00:42:37,853 --> 00:42:40,922
不, 那样你将永远无法离开.
you would never be allowed to leave. No.

593
00:42:40,956 --> 00:42:43,724
我们最大的希望... 或者说惟一的希望...
Our best hope-- our only hope--

594
00:42:43,759 --> 00:42:47,061
便是你能在战场上击败对手.
is that you can defeat them in the field.

595
00:42:47,096 --> 00:42:49,130
如果我战败?
And if I lose?

596
00:42:49,164 --> 00:42:51,699
你知道坦格利安家孩子们的下场吗...
Do you know what happened to the Targaryen children

597
00:42:51,733 --> 00:42:54,737
- 当君临城陷的时候? - 他们在睡梦中被屠杀.
- when the Mad King fell? - They were butchered in their sleep.

598
00:42:54,771 --> 00:42:57,472
是泰温兰尼斯特下的命令.
On the orders of Tywin Lannister.

599
00:42:57,507 --> 00:43:00,210
多年的时光并没有使他变仁慈一点.
And the years have not made him kinder.

600
00:43:03,313 --> 00:43:05,483
如果你战败,
If you lose,

601
00:43:05,516 --> 00:43:08,219
你的父亲会死,
your father dies,

602
00:43:08,253 --> 00:43:09,786
你的妹妹们也会死,
your sisters die,

603
00:43:09,820 --> 00:43:12,054
<i>我们都会死.
we die.</i>

604
00:43:14,625 --> 00:43:16,659
好吧, 那事情就简单了.
Well, that makes it simple then.

605
00:43:17,994 --> 00:43:19,994
我想是这样.
I suppose it does.

606
00:43:43,016 --> 00:43:46,251
现在最好由波隆和我两个过去.
From here it might be best if Bronn and I continue alone.

607
00:43:46,286 --> 00:43:48,856
对泰温之子提利昂来说最好.
Best for Tyrion son of Tywin.

608
00:43:48,889 --> 00:43:50,891
对我们来说可不好.
Not best for me.

609
00:43:50,925 --> 00:43:54,094
如果半人背叛我们,
If the half man betrays us,

610
00:43:54,128 --> 00:43:57,565
多夫之子夏嘎就会剁掉他的命根子...
Shagga Son of Dolf will cut off his manhood--

611
00:43:57,599 --> 00:44:00,135
拿去喂山羊, 我知道.
and feed it to the goats, yes.

612
00:44:02,639 --> 00:44:05,206
那好吧.
All right then.

613
00:44:05,240 --> 00:44:07,443
我要去见我父亲了.
Time to meet my father.

614
00:44:39,775 --> 00:44:42,577
- 提利昂. - 叔叔.
- Tyrion. - Uncle.

615
00:44:42,612 --> 00:44:44,480
父亲.
Father.

616
00:44:45,983 --> 00:44:48,983
看来关于你已死的传言不攻自破了.
The rumors of your demise were unfounded.

617
00:44:49,018 --> 00:44:52,420
真抱歉让您失望了.
Sorry to disappoint you.

618
00:44:52,454 --> 00:44:54,989
这些是什么人...
And who are these...

619
00:44:55,023 --> 00:44:57,257
<i>你的同伴?
Companions of yours?</i>

620
00:44:59,327 --> 00:45:01,760
这位是多夫之子夏嘎,
This is Shagga Son of Dolf,

621
00:45:01,795 --> 00:45:04,164
<i>石鸦部的酋长.
Chieftain of the Stone Crows.</i>

622
00:45:04,197 --> 00:45:08,568
<i>提魅之子提魅, 灼人部的首领.
Timett Son of Timett, ruler of the Burned Men.</i>

623
00:45:08,601 --> 00:45:13,340
<i>这位美少女是齐克之女齐拉
This fair maid is Chella daughter of Cheyk,</i>

624
00:45:13,373 --> 00:45:15,742
<i>黑耳部的领袖.
leader of the Black Ears.</i>

625
00:45:15,777 --> 00:45:19,146
而这位是波隆, 谁人之子来着...
And here we have Bronn son of...

626
00:45:19,181 --> 00:45:21,782
你不会认识他的.
You wouldn't know him.

627
00:45:23,786 --> 00:45:26,355
可否允许我为各位介绍我的父亲大人,
May I present My Lord Father,

628
00:45:26,389 --> 00:45:29,023
兰尼斯特家族的泰陀斯之子泰温,
Tywin son of Tytos of House Lannister,

629
00:45:29,059 --> 00:45:32,126
<i>凯岩城主暨西境守护.
Lord of Casterly Rock and Warden of the West?</i>

630
00:45:34,097 --> 00:45:36,733
非常感谢您为我出兵打仗.
Kind of you to go to war for me.

631
00:45:39,769 --> 00:45:41,704
你使我们别无选择.
You left us no choice.

632
00:45:41,739 --> 00:45:43,806
这事关家族的荣誉.
The honor of the House was at stake.

633
00:45:45,309 --> 00:45:48,478
你哥哥詹姆绝不会如此轻易地束手就擒的.
Your brother would never have submitted to capture so meekly.

634
00:45:48,512 --> 00:45:51,047
我们确实有所不同, 詹姆和我.
We have our differences, Jaime and I.

635
00:45:51,081 --> 00:45:53,250
他更勇敢. 而我更帅气.
He's braver. I'm better looking.

636
00:45:53,284 --> 00:45:55,619
他满身都是荣耀.
He's been covering himself in glory.

637
00:45:55,653 --> 00:45:58,889
詹姆在金牙城外击溃了三河诸侯,
Jaime smashed the River Lords at the Golden Tooth,

638
00:45:58,923 --> 00:46:02,592
现在正在围攻奔流城, 凯特琳史塔克的老家.
and now lays siege to Riverrun, Catelyn Stark's homeland.

639
00:46:02,626 --> 00:46:04,728
史塔克家在做什么? 艾德大人?
And the Starks? Lord Eddard?

640
00:46:04,762 --> 00:46:08,831
--现在是我们的人质. 他在地牢里无法带兵打仗.
--Is our hostage. He will lead no armies from his dungeon cell.

641
00:46:08,867 --> 00:46:10,900
我那美丽的姐姐是怎么说服国王
How did my sweet sister persuade the King

642
00:46:10,934 --> 00:46:12,802
囚禁他亲爱的朋友奈德的?
to imprison his dear friend Ned?

643
00:46:12,838 --> 00:46:16,807
劳勃拜拉席恩死了. 如今是乔佛里在君临执政.
Robert Baratheon is dead. Joffrey rules in King's Landing.

644
00:46:19,813 --> 00:46:21,780
你的意思是说是我姐姐在执政.
My sister rules, you mean.

645
00:46:22,983 --> 00:46:25,284
史塔克的儿子已经下令召集封臣.
Stark's son has called his banners.

646
00:46:25,318 --> 00:46:28,755
- 他正带着一支大军南下. - 不过是个毛头小子.
- He moves south with a strong host. - A green boy.

647
00:46:28,789 --> 00:46:30,556
等他尝到战斗的滋味就会...
One taste of battle and he'll run

648
00:46:30,590 --> 00:46:33,159
夹着尾巴逃回临冬城.
back to Winterfell wi his tail between his legs.

649
00:46:34,362 --> 00:46:35,862
也许吧.
Maybe.

650
00:46:35,896 --> 00:46:38,465
不过那小子确实很好战.
Though the boy does have a certain belligerence.

651
00:46:38,498 --> 00:46:41,001
你会喜欢他的.
You'd like him.

652
00:46:41,034 --> 00:46:45,072
既然我们说到打仗的事情,
While we're on the subject of war,

653
00:46:45,106 --> 00:46:47,807
我对这几位朋友做过承诺
I made promises to my friends here

654
00:46:47,842 --> 00:46:50,210
而兰尼斯特有债必还.
and a Lannister always pays his debts.

655
00:46:50,244 --> 00:46:53,313
<i>我们需要三千个头盔和盾牌,
We shall require 3,000 helms and shields,</i>

656
00:46:53,347 --> 00:46:55,581
还有刀剑, 长枪,
plus swords, pikes,

657
00:46:55,615 --> 00:46:57,416
护甲, 钉锤...
gorgets, maces--

658
00:46:57,451 --> 00:47:00,018
如果大人同意,
if it please My Lord,

659
00:47:00,052 --> 00:47:02,121
亚当爵士要我来报告, 北境军队
Ser Addam bids me report that the Northmen

660
00:47:02,155 --> 00:47:03,554
已经越过了颈泽.
have crossed the neck.

661
00:47:05,557 --> 00:47:08,025
小狼就要钻进狮口了.
The wolf rushes into the lion's jaws.

662
00:47:08,059 --> 00:47:12,297
好吧. 凯冯, 立刻下令敲鼓集合.
So be it. Kevan, command the drummers beat assembly.

663
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:16,936
并送信给詹姆说我将前去同罗柏史塔克决战.
And send word to Jaime that I am moving against Robb Stark.

664
00:47:16,969 --> 00:47:18,938
遵命, 大人.
At once, My Lord.

665
00:47:31,887 --> 00:47:34,855
听说山地部落的人都是伟大的战士.
It is said that the men of the Mountain clans are great warriors.

666
00:47:34,889 --> 00:47:36,623
与我一同出兵作战
Ride with me against my enemies

667
00:47:36,657 --> 00:47:39,693
你们将得到我儿子承诺的一切, 甚至更多.
and you shall have all my son promised you and more.

668
00:47:39,728 --> 00:47:41,963
但这个半人得跟我们一起作战.
Only if the half man fights with us.

669
00:47:41,998 --> 00:47:45,434
直到我们拿到他答应的武器,
Until we hold the steel he pledged us,

670
00:47:45,469 --> 00:47:47,869
这小狮子的命是我们的.
the little lion's life is ours.

671
00:47:53,443 --> 00:47:56,112
<i>斥候报告说泰温大人正在北上.
Rodrik: The scouts report Lord Tywin moves north.</i>

672
00:47:56,146 --> 00:47:57,980
我们需要凭借险要地形截住他,
We need to get him on broken ground,

673
00:47:58,014 --> 00:47:59,681
使他的骑士无法发挥力量.
put his Knights at a disadvantage.

674
00:47:59,715 --> 00:48:01,818
不, 我们要从他侧面绕过去
No, we need to get around him

675
00:48:01,851 --> 00:48:04,753
并打破詹姆兰尼斯特对奔流城的围攻.
and break Jaime Lannister's siege of Riverrun.

676
00:48:04,789 --> 00:48:07,623
这样三河诸候就会加入我们的队伍.
Do that and the River Lords will join us.

677
00:48:07,657 --> 00:48:09,525
无论怎样做我们都需要先过绿叉河
To do either we need to cross the river

678
00:48:09,559 --> 00:48:11,226
而孪河城是过河的惟一路线.
and the only crossing is at The Twins.

679
00:48:11,260 --> 00:48:13,295
<i>佛雷大人控制着孪河桥.
Theon: Lord Frey controls that bridge.</i>

680
00:48:13,329 --> 00:48:14,896
他是你父亲的封臣.
Your father's bannerman.

681
00:48:14,931 --> 00:48:18,166
我父亲称他为 "迟到的佛雷大人"
"The late Lord Frey" my father calls him.

682
00:48:18,201 --> 00:48:21,704
当年三叉戟河之战, 他在战斗结束后才现身.
At the Trident, he didn't appear until the battle was done.

683
00:48:21,737 --> 00:48:25,775
不是每个人都把自己的誓言当回事的.
Some men takes their oaths more seriously than others.

684
00:48:27,744 --> 00:48:30,278
( Grunting )

685
00:48:33,182 --> 00:48:35,918
罗柏说得对. 我们需要那座桥.
Robb's right. We need that bridge.

686
00:48:35,952 --> 00:48:38,052
那么该怎么办?
So what's it going to be?

687
00:48:38,088 --> 00:48:41,489
我们先对付詹姆还是泰温?
Do we move against Jaime or Lord Tywin?

688
00:48:45,661 --> 00:48:47,195
打扰了, 大人.
Your pardon, my lords.

689
00:48:47,230 --> 00:48:49,898
<i>我们抓住了一个兰尼斯特军的斥候.
We've captured a Lannister scout.</i>

690
00:48:51,802 --> 00:48:55,137
别担心, 小伙子. 他不会活着离开这个帐篷.
Don't worry, lad. He won't b  leaving this tent with his head.

691
00:48:56,474 --> 00:48:58,141
你们在哪儿发现他的?
Where did you find him?

692
00:48:58,175 --> 00:49:00,309
在营地周围的树丛里.
In the brush above the encampment.

693
00:49:00,344 --> 00:49:02,211
<i>他好象正在估算人数.
He looked to be counting.</i>

694
00:49:12,657 --> 00:49:14,458
你算出来有多少人?
How high did you get?

695
00:49:16,827 --> 00:49:18,829
两万. 或许更多.
20,000. Maybe more.

696
00:49:19,864 --> 00:49:21,597
你不必自己动手行刑.
You don't have to do this yourself.

697
00:49:21,632 --> 00:49:23,199
您父亲会理解的...
Your father would understand--

698
00:49:23,233 --> 00:49:27,269
我父亲懂得仁慈, 如果不是非杀不可.
My father unrstands mercy, when there is room for it.

699
00:49:28,672 --> 00:49:30,505
他也懂得荣誉...
And he understands honor...

700
00:49:33,311 --> 00:49:35,577
和勇气.
and courage.

701
00:49:37,481 --> 00:49:39,315
放他走吧.
Let him go.

702
00:49:40,284 --> 00:49:42,684
罗柏.
Robb.

703
00:49:54,697 --> 00:49:57,664
去告诉泰温大人, 凛冬将至.
( Softly ) Tell Lord Tywin Winter is coming for him.

704
00:49:57,699 --> 00:50:02,635
两万北境大军正在南下, 看看他是不是真的能拉金屎.
20,000 Northerners marching south to find out if he really does shit gold.

705
00:50:04,706 --> 00:50:06,206
遵命, 大人.
Yes, My Lord.

706
00:50:06,239 --> 00:50:08,041
多谢, 大人.
Thank you, My Lord.

707
00:50:17,485 --> 00:50:21,188
你疯了吗, 孩子?! 放他走?
Are you touched, boy?! Letting him go?

708
00:50:21,222 --> 00:50:23,257
你又称我孩子了.
You call me boy again.

709
00:50:24,760 --> 00:50:26,393
下去吧.
Go on.

710
00:50:35,570 --> 00:50:36,802
( Growls )

711
00:50:43,409 --> 00:50:46,612
喂.
Oi.

712
00:50:51,684 --> 00:50:54,353
<i>国王陛下决定...
Pycelle: It is also the wish of His Grace</i>

713
00:50:54,387 --> 00:50:59,693
<i>尽忠职守的杰诺斯史林特,
that his loyal servant Janos Slynt,</i>

714
00:50:59,726 --> 00:51:02,829
<i>- 都城守卫队司令... - 艾伦爵士.
- Commander of the City Watch... - Ser Aron.</i>

715
00:51:02,864 --> 00:51:06,434
<i>立刻擢升为贵族...
...Be at once raised to the rank of Lord...</i>

716
00:51:06,467 --> 00:51:11,938
<i>- 盖尔斯大人. - ...赐予古老的赫伦堡,
- Lord Gyles. - ...And granted the ancient seat of Harrenhal,</i>

717
00:51:11,972 --> 00:51:15,809
<i>其子嗣将世代继承此等荣耀
and that his sons and grandsons shall hold this honor</i>

718
00:51:15,842 --> 00:51:20,947
<i>直到世界末日.
after him until the end of time.</i>

719
00:51:20,981 --> 00:51:23,481
( Lords mutter )

720
00:51:24,784 --> 00:51:28,119
为取代叛徒艾德史塔克,
In the place of the traitor Eddard Stark,

721
00:51:28,153 --> 00:51:32,824
<i>国王陛下决定由泰温兰尼斯特,
it is the wish of his Grace that Tywin Lannister,</i>

722
00:51:32,858 --> 00:51:36,661
<i>凯岩城主暨西境守护,
Lord of Casterly Rock and Warden of the West,</i>

723
00:51:36,695 --> 00:51:40,798
<i>担任国王之手.
be appointed Hand of the King.</i>

724
00:51:40,833 --> 00:51:42,733
最后,
Lastly,

725
00:51:42,768 --> 00:51:45,603
于此密谋四起, 动乱不堪之际,
in these times of treason and turmoil,

726
00:51:45,637 --> 00:51:48,873
<i>御前会议认为...
it is the view of the Council</i>

727
00:51:48,907 --> 00:51:54,144
乔佛里国王的生命安全
that the life and safety

728
00:51:51,476 --> 00:51:54,144
of King Joffrey

729
00:51:54,179 --> 00:51:58,416
实乃第一要务.
be of paramount importance.

730
00:52:00,018 --> 00:52:02,552
巴利斯坦赛尔弥爵士.
Ser Barristan Selmy.

731
00:52:08,893 --> 00:52:12,396
陛下, 我听候您的差遣.
Your Grace, I am yours to command.

732
00:52:12,431 --> 00:52:14,532
请起, 巴利斯坦爵士.
Rise, Ser Barristan.

733
00:52:15,402 --> 00:52:17,503
你可以卸下头盔了.
You may remove your helm.

734
00:52:22,443 --> 00:52:25,045
<i>长久以来你为国效命，尽忠职守.
You have served the Realm long and faithfully.</i>

735
00:52:25,079 --> 00:52:29,050
<i>七国上下每个人都对你心怀感激.
Every man and woman in the Seven Kingdoms owes you thanks.</i>

736
00:52:29,085 --> 00:52:32,353
然而是时候让你卸下你的铠甲和宝剑了.
But it is time to put aside your armor and your sword.

737
00:52:32,387 --> 00:52:35,289
<i>你该安享晚年, 并自豪地回顾...
It is time to rest and look back with pride</i>

738
00:52:35,324 --> 00:52:36,958
你长久以来的功绩了.
on your many years of service.

739
00:52:36,992 --> 00:52:39,126
<i>( Murmuring )</i>

740
00:52:39,161 --> 00:52:41,596
陛下, 御林铁卫乃是宣誓效命的兄弟.
Your Grace, the Kingsguard is a sworn brotherhood.

741
00:52:41,630 --> 00:52:43,797
<i>我们必须终身守誓.
Our vows are taken for life.</i>

742
00:52:43,833 --> 00:52:46,335
惟有一死才能解除我们的神圣使命.
Only death relieves us of our sacred trust.

743
00:52:46,369 --> 00:52:50,072
是谁的死, 巴利斯坦爵士? 是你还是你的国王?
Whose death, Ser Barristan? Yours or your King's?

744
00:52:50,106 --> 00:52:52,974
<i>我父亲的死就是你的责任.
Joffrey: You let my father die.</i>

745
00:52:53,009 --> 00:52:55,945
你太老了, 谁都保护不了.
You're too old to protect anybody.

746
00:52:58,248 --> 00:53:00,983
- 陛下-- - 御前会议已经决定
- Your Grace-- - The Council has determined

747
00:53:01,018 --> 00:53:03,452
由詹姆兰尼斯特爵士接替你的职务
that Ser Jaime Lannister will take your place

748
00:53:03,487 --> 00:53:05,755
<i>担任御林铁卫队长.
as Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.</i>

749
00:53:05,789 --> 00:53:07,324
那个人玷污了自己的宝剑
The man who profaned his blade

750
00:53:07,358 --> 00:53:09,559
杀死了他宣誓要保护的国王!
with the blood of the King he had sworn to defend!

751
00:53:09,594 --> 00:53:11,527
小心一点, 爵士.
Careful, Ser.

752
00:53:11,561 --> 00:53:13,262
我们并非不知感恩
We have nothing but gratitude

753
00:53:13,297 --> 00:53:15,766
您的长期贡献有目共睹, 爵士.
for your long service, good Ser.

754
00:53:15,800 --> 00:53:18,268
您将得到一座坚固的海滨城堡,
You shall be given a stout Keep beside the sea,

755
00:53:18,302 --> 00:53:20,637
以及满足您需要的大批仆役.
with servants to look after your every need.

756
00:53:20,670 --> 00:53:22,871
给我一个养老的地方
A hall to die in

757
00:53:22,907 --> 00:53:25,307
<i>以及为我送终的人.
and men to bury me.</i>

758
00:53:26,909 --> 00:53:29,945
我既生为一名骑士.
I am a Knight.

759
00:53:29,980 --> 00:53:33,016
也要死得像个骑士.
I shall die a Knight.

760
00:53:38,956 --> 00:53:41,090
像个没穿衣服的骑士, 是吧.
A naked Knight, apparently.

761
00:53:41,125 --> 00:53:43,260
( Laughter )

762
00:53:52,235 --> 00:53:55,672
即便现在我仍可以像切蛋糕一样把你们五个通通砍倒!
Even now I could cut through the five of you like carving a cake!

763
00:53:59,844 --> 00:54:02,378
拿去, 小子!
Here, boy!

764
00:54:02,413 --> 00:54:04,847
把它熔了加到铁王座上吧.
Melt it down and add it to the others.

765
00:54:19,362 --> 00:54:21,329
<i>( Doors creak, clang )</i>

766
00:54:21,364 --> 00:54:23,699
如果在场各位还有其他事...
If any man in this hall has other matters

767
00:54:23,733 --> 00:54:26,867
请现在向国王陛下禀报
to set before His Grace, let him speak now

768
00:54:26,902 --> 00:54:30,139
否则退朝.
or go forth and hold his silence.

769
00:54:32,809 --> 00:54:34,945
陛下.
Your Grace.

770
00:54:34,978 --> 00:54:37,347
请上前来, 小姐.
Come forward, My Lady.

771
00:54:39,117 --> 00:54:41,853
<i>史塔克家族的珊莎小姐.
Steward: The Lady Sansa of House Stark.</i>

772
00:54:43,389 --> 00:54:46,791
珊莎, 你有事禀报国王陛下和御前会议?
Do you have some business for the King and the Council, Sansa?

773
00:54:46,826 --> 00:54:48,659
是的.
I do.

774
00:54:53,532 --> 00:54:56,634
启禀陛下, 我要为我父亲请求您的慈悲,
As it please Your Grace, I ask mercy for my father,

775
00:54:56,668 --> 00:55:00,137
艾德史塔克大人, 前任国王之手.
Lord Eddard Stark, who was Hand of the King.

776
00:55:00,172 --> 00:55:03,039
叛国大罪好似带毒的野草.
Treason is a noxious weed.

777
00:55:03,074 --> 00:55:07,244
- 必须连根拔除... - 让她说下去.
- It should be torn out, root-- - Let her speak.

778
00:55:07,280 --> 00:55:09,981
我要听听她的话.
I want to hear what she says.

779
00:55:10,016 --> 00:55:12,150
感谢您, 陛下.
Thank you, Your Grace.

780
00:55:12,184 --> 00:55:14,788
你要否认你父亲所犯罪行?
Do you deny your father's crime?

781
00:55:14,822 --> 00:55:19,293
不, 诸位大人. 我明白他必须接受惩罚.
No, My Lords. I know he must be punished.

782
00:55:19,327 --> 00:55:21,327
我请求的只是慈悲为怀.
All I ask is mercy.

783
00:55:21,362 --> 00:55:24,231
<i>我知道我父亲必定对其所为懊悔不已.
I know My Lord father must regret what he did.</i>

784
00:55:24,266 --> 00:55:26,568
他是劳勃国王的好友, 他敬爱国王.
He was King Robert's friend and he loved him.

785
00:55:26,601 --> 00:55:28,802
你们知道他是真心敬爱他.
You all know he loved him.

786
00:55:28,838 --> 00:55:32,440
他从未想当国王之手, 直到国王要求他.
He never wanted to be Hand until the King asked him.

787
00:55:32,474 --> 00:55:35,876
他必定是受人蛊惑... 蓝礼大人或史坦尼斯大人
They must have lied to him-- Lord Renly or Lord Stannis

788
00:55:35,909 --> 00:55:38,711
或是其他什么人. 他们欺骗了他!
or somebody. They must have lied!

789
00:55:38,746 --> 00:55:41,215
他说我不是国王.
He said I wasn't the King.

790
00:55:41,248 --> 00:55:43,315
他为什么要那样说?
Why did he say that?

791
00:55:43,351 --> 00:55:45,619
他受了重伤.
He was badly hurt.

792
00:55:45,652 --> 00:55:48,521
派席尔大学士给他服用了罂粟花奶.
Maester Pycelle was giving him milk of the poppy.

793
00:55:48,554 --> 00:55:52,724
当时他神智不清. 否则他绝不会那样说的.
He wasn't himself. Otherwise h  never would have said it.

794
00:55:55,061 --> 00:55:58,931
孩子对父亲的信赖... 多么单纯天真.
A child's faith... Such sweet innocence.

795
00:55:58,965 --> 00:56:02,635
<i>可是人们不是常说, 智慧之言往往来自
And yet they say wisdom oft comes</i>

796
00:56:02,670 --> 00:56:04,503
孩童之口么.
from the mouths of babes.

797
00:56:04,538 --> 00:56:08,675
但叛国就是叛国!
Treason is treason!

798
00:56:11,813 --> 00:56:13,980
你还有什么事?
Anything else?

799
00:56:15,550 --> 00:56:18,952
如果您心里仍然有我,
If you still have any affection in your heart for me,

800
00:56:18,985 --> 00:56:22,487
请成全我这个心愿吧, 陛下.
please do me this kindness, Your Grace.

801
00:56:32,065 --> 00:56:34,331
你的肺腑之言感动了我.
Your sweet words have moved me.

802
00:56:36,735 --> 00:56:39,302
但你父亲必须先俯首认罪.
But your father has to confess.

803
00:56:39,338 --> 00:56:42,940
他必须承认我是他的国王...
He has to confess and say that I'm the King...

804
00:56:45,842 --> 00:56:47,978
不然我无法手下留情.
Or there'll be no mercy for him.

805
00:56:52,449 --> 00:56:54,550
他一定会的.
He will.

806
00:57:01,425 --> 00:57:04,561
<i>( Music playing )</i>

807
